<C>__{old salieri}
<D>__{because you will not enter me, with all my need for you; because you scorn my attempts at virtue; because you choose for your instrument a boastful, lustful, smutty infantile boy and give me for reward only the ability to recognize the incarnation; because you are unjust, unfair, unkind, i will block you! i swear it! i will hinder and harm your creature on earth as far as i am able. i will ruin your incarnation.}
